text: Marina Tokumoto (born 2 February 1996) is a Japanese female water polo player who participated at the 2015 World Aquatics Championships, 2017 World Aquatics Championships, and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == ==Other websites == * Tokumoto Marina Asian Games Previews zimbio Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese water polo players
